{"tid":132966,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"iPhone 7 Plus 起火冒煙！事前竟曾到過 Apple Store 維修","createTime":"2017-02-24T08:15:36.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-26T11:03:54.000Z","uid":83012,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"d4613db591bf36d37d8472ed977204c9043ab206","tid":132966,"uid":83012,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-24T08:15:36.000Z","msg":"相信大家都知道，如果 iPhone 出現問題的話，應該到 Apple Store 或是到蘋果官方授權的服務商進行維修。不過日前發生了一件事，令人對這個做法也開始有所懷疑。外國媒體 Mashable 報導，近日有外國的 iPhone 7 Plus 突然起火冒出大量白煙，手機的邊緣位置脹起，螢幕與機身分離，手機所使用的保護套也被金屬殼導出的熱所融化了。但用家指出，事前這台 iPhone 7 Plus 曾到過 Apple Store 中進行測試維修<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.newmobilelife.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/02/C5Tx6IAUkAA7mcZ.jpg?w=1019&amp;ssl=1\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi0.wp.com%2Fwww.newmobilelife.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F02%2FC5Tx6IAUkAA7mcZ.jpg%3Fw%3D1019%26ssl%3D1&h=b0ddcd9c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i2.wp.com/www.newmobilelife.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/02/screenshot-2017-02-24-15.22.59.jpg?w=1030&amp;ssl=1\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi2.wp.com%2Fwww.newmobilelife.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F02%2Fscreenshot-2017-02-24-15.22.59.jpg%3Fw%3D1030%26ssl%3D1&h=08f2c968&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n消息指出，在起火前一天，iPhone 7 Plus 出現很多問題，並且無法開機，機主 Brianna Olivas 就把這台 iPhone 7 Plus 帶到當地的Apple Store 打算進行維修。可是在 Apple Store 的職員進行過一系列的測試後發現 iPhone 一切正常，而且裝置在當場也可以正常運作，於是便離開，並在當晚如常的把 iPhone 7 Plus 進行充電。可是在第二天的早上，Brianna Olivas 的男朋友手機從充電器拔出後放到桌上，事主轉身走開時，iPhone 7 Plus 就開始冒煙起火，並傳出尖銳的聲響。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i1.wp.com/www.newmobilelife.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/02/C5Tx6H_UcAEIF-_.jpg-large.jpeg?w=1536&amp;ssl=1\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi1.wp.com%2Fwww.newmobilelife.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F02%2FC5Tx6H_UcAEIF-_.jpg-large.jpeg%3Fw%3D1536%26ssl%3D1&h=fe940a71&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i1.wp.com/www.newmobilelife.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/02/C5Tx6IAUkAA7mcZ.jpg-large.jpeg?w=1536&amp;ssl=1\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi1.wp.com%2Fwww.newmobilelife.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F02%2FC5Tx6IAUkAA7mcZ.jpg-large.jpeg%3Fw%3D1536%26ssl%3D1&h=22866ad2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n當時事主在洗手間內，事主男友查看手機時，手機已經開始起火冒煙，事主迅速把手機扔到洗手機，手機開始爆炸並冒出更多的濃煙。事件發生之後，事主把 iPhone 7 Plus 轉交給蘋果，蘋果表示會對事件作出深入調查，結果將於一周後公佈。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/ext_tw_video_thumb/834556159243595776/pu/img/g1VtObG2KRhscmJQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpbs.twimg.com%2Fext_tw_video_thumb%2F834556159243595776%2Fpu%2Fimg%2Fg1VtObG2KRhscmJQ.jpg&h=a8b0f422&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"cb94067c9fe975cfa6dcff035cefd7e8c469a599","tid":132966,"uid":52215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-24T08:39:33.000Z","msg":"咁撚恐怖, 流動炸彈<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b44873a8c1d9b74ceefc8ff38d011889a1a87964","tid":132966,"uid":498,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-25T07:43:01.000Z","msg":"最後咪又係比過部新機你簽保密協議"},{"pid":"b18b91b8eb94fdd3e7246712bc7c8a9b67f58b2a","tid":132966,"uid":59920,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-25T07:44:45.000Z","msg":"用家問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ae0dad260493a17abb826ea556412111a5cae7cd","tid":132966,"uid":49,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-25T07:58:52.000Z","msg":"點解三星爆完咁大獲<br />\n冇啦啦蘋果又會爆？"},{"pid":"62c7cfc25cc55f1a73c50bcfa848279bd9d9b8b6","tid":132966,"uid":58841,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-25T12:23:29.000Z","msg":"咩叫洗手機"},{"pid":"89df24107c8ab79c3c6ead55862db7bd368b6de1","tid":132966,"uid":83012,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-25T12:24:14.000Z","msg":"最下面本身係片黎，唔知點解Post唔到上黎"},{"pid":"938c7a281ddd47ea37f989908e0aa18e1d3d2478","tid":132966,"uid":83012